        The avatars (the small pictures by some of the posts) are from <a href="www.gravatar.com">Gravatar</a>, if you have a <a href="www.gravatar.com">Gravatar</a> associated with the e-mail address you signed up for My World To Go with then it will automatically be used.</div>

